Lauren Vélez https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lauren_V%C3%A9lez 0 Lauren Luna Vélez, sometimes credited as Luna Lauren Velez or just Luna Vélez, (born November 2, 1964) is an American actress and the twin sister of actress Lorraine Vélez. Her most notable roles are as María LaGuerta on Showtime's Dexter, Detective Nina Moreno on Fox's New York Undercover, Dr. Gloria Nathan on HBO's prison drama Oz, and Elena on ABC's comedy-drama Ugly Betty.
